Firedrill decides to follow the rest of the Maximals on. He wondered
where his buddies were.

Cliffjumper keeps his eye on Torca and Klant, not sure what they were up
to, (They havent moved in a few days). He then hears the roar of another
engine behind him, and sighs, knowing that Beachcomber will have given
him away. "Okay, hands up, who are you?" He asks, jumping out from
behind a rock, and pointing his blaster at the two Maximals.
